body:
Ant provides a notification system that doesn't need to have any state management or DOM management. There is no work to do here. Simple call the notification function from Ant.

```
notification.open({
    message: 'Notification Title',
    description: 'This is the content of the notification. This is the content of the notification. This is the content of the notification.',
});
```

